last_episode_to_air.name: Do I?
last_episode_to_air.overview: Regina and Bennie are forced to help a newly single Tasha get back on her feet. Major doubts linger for Lucretia and Frank as the big day approaches.

name: The Upshaws
overview: Bennie Upshaw, the head of a Black working class family in Indianapolis, is a charming, well-intentioned mechanic and lifelong mess just trying his best to step up and care for his family and tolerate his sardonic sister-in-law, all without a blueprint for success.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: A working-class Black family in Indiana strives for a better life and a happy home while juggling everyday struggles in this comedy series.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Bennie, Regina and Lucretia are back to their usual antics. But will new problems and trust issues keep them from holding the family together? Still striving for success and surviving every mess, the Upshaws face a series of obstacles that put their resilience — and relationships — to the test.

tagline: They're back and as imperfect as ever.

episodes.name: Birthday B.S.
episodes.overview: When two of his kids have birthday parties on the same day, Bennie scrambles to find a venue for one, then bounces back and forth between both events.

episodes.name: The Hook-Up
episodes.overview: After meeting the manager of an upscale restaurant, Bennie takes Regina out hoping to break their dry spell but realizes the meal isn't on the house.

episodes.name: Joy Ride
episodes.overview: A customer entrusts his sleek ride with its secret compartment to Bennie. Duck overstays his welcome at the Upshaw residence. Regina eyes a promotion.

episodes.name: Big Plans
episodes.overview: As Regina tries to land a better job at a different organization, Bennie’s friends get in his ear about her looking to level up her life without him.

episodes.name: Ridin' Dirty
episodes.overview: Regina juggles family duties with work and studying for the GMAT, but Bennie doesn’t help lighten the load — and she reaches a boiling point.

episodes.name: Last Straw
episodes.overview: When Tasha gets into an accident, Bennie comes up with a solution — without telling Regina. Meanwhile, conflicts erupt between other family members.

episodes.name: Yard Sale
episodes.overview: After Regina throws Bennie out, she starts cleaning house. Bennie tries his old tricks to get back in her good graces. Lucretia's affair takes a turn.

episodes.name: Night Out
episodes.overview: Regina goes to her work party solo while Bennie has his own fun with the guys. Lucretia and Bennie get drunk together, and Bernard reveals his truth.

episodes.name: Gloves Off
episodes.overview: When Bennie tries to live a healthier lifestyle, he winds up in a boxing ring with an emotional Bernard. Maya struggles with a school bully.

episodes.name: The Backslide
episodes.overview: With Bennie back in the house and bonding more with the kids, Regina's frustrations start to show. After she takes the GMAT, the family comes together.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: A working-class Black family in Indiana strives for a better life and a happy home while juggling everyday struggles in this comedy series.

episodes.name: Maybe Daddy
episodes.overview: When a surprise comes knocking on the family’s front door, Regina points the finger at Bennie and pushes Bernard to wise up.

episodes.name: Bennie's Woman
episodes.overview: A suspicious Lucretia conducts a thorough investigation. Meanwhile, a big misunderstanding leads to a bigger mistake as Bennie attempts to close a deal.

episodes.name: Testing, Testing
episodes.overview: When Regina retakes the GMAT, Lucretia struggles to keep order in the house. Bennie and the crew scramble to get the shop up to code for an inspection.

episodes.name: Control Issues
episodes.overview: Regina is determined to throw a budget-friendly birthday party for Maya until Lucretia takes over. Bennie tries to bribe his way out of a lawsuit.

episodes.name: Duct Up
episodes.overview: Regina plots to win over her boss at work. Lucretia dines with an old flame. Bennie lands in a tight spot. The kids are left to look after themselves.

episodes.name: New Growth
episodes.overview: A crisis forces Regina to seek out Tasha's services. At the shop, Lucretia tries to talk sense into Bennie. Aaliyah and Maya have a sibling squabble.

episodes.name: Sista, Sista
episodes.overview: With their unfiltered sister in town, Lucretia and Regina let a few things off their chests. Not to be outdone by Noah, Bennie makes a pricey purchase.

episodes.name: Goin' In
episodes.overview: After their blowout, Lucretia takes time for herself while Regina gets fed up at work. Bennie fears he's losing Kelvin. All drama leads back to the shop.

episodes.name: The Unforgiven
episodes.overview: With Bennie and Lucretia in a pinch, a jobless Regina must drum up cash fast — and try to hide the situation from the kids.

episodes.name: Home Repairs
episodes.overview: Frustrated with his job at the garage, Bennie starts a new business closer to home. Aaliyah yearns to fit in. Bernard's relationship hits a bump.

episodes.name: Treading Water
episodes.overview: After running into a roadblock on her job search, Regina takes advantage of funemployment. Bennie gets a fancy new gig, and Aaliyah seeks a new friend.

episodes.name: Off Beat
episodes.overview: In need of a break, Regina crashes Lucretia's homecoming weekend. Bernard attempts to connect with his daughter. Aaliyah deals with a friendship breakup.

episodes.name: Lane Change
episodes.overview: Regina makes adjustments at her new job. Aaliyah believes Maya is possessed and sets out to film her. Kelvin’s return causes friction among the family.

episodes.name: Heart Wants
episodes.overview: After having a strange dream, Regina thinks of what could have been. Lucretia receives a tempting offer. Bennie's back issues cause problems at the shop.

episodes.name: Heart Matters
episodes.overview: An unexpected crisis puts the family on edge and forces Regina to take a pause. Meanwhile, Lucretia and Bennie handle responsibilities at home.

episodes.name: Now What
episodes.overview: The family sends Regina off as she takes on a new endeavor, but a sudden change of plans has Lucretia and Bennie worried about her — and the future.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Bennie, Regina and Lucretia are back to their usual antics. But will new problems and trust issues keep them from holding the family together? Still striving for success and surviving every mess, the Upshaws face a series of obstacles that put their resilience — and relationships — to the test.

episodes.name: Thera Please
episodes.overview: In the aftermath of her heart attack, Regina attempts to bring Bennie to therapy with her. An overwhelmed Lucretia starts to miss having her own space.

episodes.name: Need Change
episodes.overview: Lucretia receives life-changing news after agreeing to fund Bernard's business. When therapy with Bennie uncovers hard truths, Regina has a breakthrough.

episodes.name: Forbidden Fruit
episodes.overview: A hot-headed Bernard teaches Aaliyah how to drive. Regina and Bennie find new thrills in sneaky rendezvous. Lucretia tries to resell gifts for money.

episodes.name: Slap Happy
episodes.overview: Aaliyah continues to shun Regina. A turn of events gives Lucretia cause for celebration, but not for long. Bennie acts fast when Kelvin lands in trouble.

episodes.name: Really, Mama?
episodes.overview: A surprise visitor puts Bennie's loyalties to the test. Lucretia secures a new source of income that makes her circumstances more challenging.

episodes.name: Auto Motives
episodes.overview: Now flush with cash, Bennie splurges on a gift for the kids that stirs up tension with Bernard. At a crossroads, Lucretia weighs a difficult decision.

episodes.name: Hail Mary
episodes.overview: With the shop and their finances in jeopardy, Bennie and Lucretia search high and low for a solution and potential buyer. Is the family business a wrap?

episodes.name: Electric Feels
episodes.overview: The family adjusts to their new living situation. Bennie works to get his electric vehicle certification. Aaliyah tries to keep her boyfriend a secret.

episodes.name: Background Checkered
episodes.overview: Bennie meddles in Aaliyah's relationship, sparking memories of him meeting Regina's parents. Maya's school play about Black history riles Lucretia up.

episodes.name: Girl Trouble
episodes.overview: Regina attempts to make good with an old rival for Aaliyah's sake. A heartbroken Tony seeks help from Bennie as he steps back into the dating scene.

episodes.name: Ain't Broke
episodes.overview: Lucretia takes a big leap — but Regina worries her sister's making a big decision for the wrong reasons. Bennie pushes a nervous Bernard to open his gym.

episodes.name: Do I?
episodes.overview: Regina and Bennie are forced to help a newly single Tasha get back on her feet. Major doubts linger for Lucretia and Frank as the big day approaches.
